## üé® Design System & Consistency

### üö® CRITICAL RULE: Design Consistency

**ALL pages must maintain visual consistency with the landing page.**

Reference: `creator-osx-mvp/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`

#### Required Standards:
- **Colors**: Use slate (not gray) for neutrals, brand-500 (#0ea5e9 sky blue) for primary actions
- **Typography**: Inter for body, Playfair Display for serif headings
- **Spacing**: Use Tailwind's 4px scale (gap-4, p-6, etc.)
- **Shadows**: Subtle only (shadow-sm to shadow-xl)
- **Borders**: Always use border-slate-100 for cards
- **Status Colors**: Follow defined palette (blue, yellow, orange, green, red, purple, gray)

#### Quick Reference:
```jsx
// Primary Button
<button className="px-6 py-3 bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600 text-white rounded-lg">

// Card
<div className="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-100 p-6 shadow-sm">

// Text
<h1 className="text-slate-900">  // Primary text
<p className="text-slate-700">   // Body text
<span className="text-slate-500"> // Secondary text
```

### Design Inspiration

- **Notion** - Minimal, clean interface
- **Linear** - Fast, keyboard-first UX
- **Height** - Pipeline management
- **Airtable** - Flexible data views

